a:17:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";s:11:"small_descr";s:130:"Rogaine 2% is used to treat male pattern baldness in patients who are experiencing gradually thinning hair on the top of the head.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:116:"Rogain 2% dient der Behandlung von männlichem Haarausfall bei Patienten, deren Haaren sich schrittweise verdünnen.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:136:"Rogaine 2% est utilisé pour traiter la calvitie masculine aux patients qui éprouvent l'éclaircie des cheveux sur le haut de la tête.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:159:"Rogaine 2% es usado para tratar alopecia masculina en los pacientes que experimentan adelgazamiento gradualmente del cabello en la parte superior de la cabeza.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:162:"Rogaine 2% si usa per curare la caduta dei capelli di modello maschile in pazienti che stanno provando capelli gradualmente assottiglianti sulla cima della testa.";s:10:"full_descr";s:2888:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Rogaine is used to treat male pattern baldness in patients who are experiencing gradually thinning hair on the top of the head.<br />Rogaine may also be used for other purposes.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Apply the prescribed amount, usually 1 mL, to the affected areas of the scalp. Rogaine is usually applied twice daily, in the morning and at night.<br />Wash your hands after applying Rogaine.<br />Avoid getting Rogaine in the eyes, nose, or mouth. If this occurs, rinse the area with water.<br />&nbsp;Do not use Rogaine if the skin on your scalp is damaged, irritated, or sunburned. This may allow more of the medication to be absorbed by your body, which could be dangerous. Do not use more than 2 mL of Rogaine in one day. More medication will not increase or hasten hair growth but it may cause dangerous side effects.&nbsp;<br />Do not use Rogaine on any part of your body other than your scalp. Application to other body parts can be dangerous.<br />It may take 4 months or more before new hair growth is seen. New hair is usually soft, colorless, and barely visible. With further treatment, the hair will become similar in color and thickness to existing hair.<br />If no hair growth is seen after 4 months of treatment, discontinuation of Rogaine should be considered.<br />If treatment is discontinued, new hair growth will usually be shed within a few months.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store Rogaine at room temperature away from moisture and heat.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>Do not use Rogaine if the skin on your scalp is damaged, irritated, or sunburned. This may allow more of the medication to be absorbed by your body, which could be dangerous. <br />Before using Rogaine tell your doctor if you have heart disease. Minoxidil absorbed by the body can affect the heart.<br /> Rogaine is in the FDA pregnancy category C. This means that it is not known whether Rogaine will be harmful to an unborn to baby. Do not use Rogaine without first talking to your doctor if you are pregnant or could become pregnant during treatment. Minoxidil may affect a nursing baby. Do not use this medication without first talking to your doctor if you are breast-feeding a baby.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>If you experience any of the following serious side effects, stop using this medication and seek emergency medical attention:&nbsp;<br />an allergic reaction (difficulty breathing; closing of the throat; swelling of the lips, tongue, or face; or hives);<br />chest pain; irregular or very fast heartbeats; dizziness or lightheadedness; or fainting.<br />Continue to use Rogaine and talk to your doctor when it is convenient if you experience<br />itching, redness, dryness, or flaking of the scalp; or a headache.<br />Side effects other than those listed here may also occur.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:9:"26.467056";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"flacons";s:4:"type";s:2:"ml";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:10:{i:4861;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4861";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"34.3728";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4862;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4862";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"29.98072";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4863;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4863";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"28.51669";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4864;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4864";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"27.78468";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4865;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4865";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"27.34547";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4866;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4866";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"27.05267";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4867;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4867";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.84352";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4868;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4868";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.68666";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4869;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4869";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.56466";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}i:4870;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4870";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.46706";s:4:"name";s:9:"Rogaine 2";}}}}